data.description: Discover the allure of this colonial treasure in Beth. Twp, nestled on a grand corner lot. A home where warmth meets modern efficiency, boasting $39K solar panels for energy savings. Step inside to an open foyer leading to a spacious living room, bathed in light, blending timeless charm and contemporary comfort. Every window in this gem has been replaced with premium Anderson windows. The spacious dining room is perfect for festive feasts and cozy dinners. Next to it, a chef-friendly kitchen with ample counters invites culinary explorations and socializing and nearby, a seating area offers peaceful coffee mornings and serene book evenings. Tucked away on the first floor is a family room, a cozy haven on winter nights with its crackling wood-burning fireplace, flowing out to a composite deck and a backyard oasis. A gazebo stands guard over a tranquil fishpond, while a paver path leads to the glistening above-ground pool. A fire pit calls for starlit conversations, and a fenced yard ensures privacy and serenity. Upstairs, the magic continues with three bedrooms, including a large owner's suite complete with ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet. The partially finished basement, a treasure trove of potential, offers storage space and a utility room housing a new washer and dryer. Each corner, each room holds a story, a memory, a promise of new beginnings, now echoed in its eco-friendly enhancements and upgrades. Will you be the one to continue its legacy?
